Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98244,99537}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101289,102707}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102707,104709}I know your escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113384,114636}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120725,121934}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123102,126898}Today is the day\NI'm going to capture you on film!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127398,129359}What? Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146167,148795}Hey… What are you\Nsmiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148795,150588}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155343,158262}What's with this article,\NSaruwatari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158262,162308}What do you mean?\NI just reported the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163142,164852}You call these facts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164852,167730}First of all, if you hadn't interfered,\NSt. Tail would have been…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167730,170900}Ah, she escaped\Nfrom you again, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170900,172694}What a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173611,174862}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174862,177115}I'll definitely catch her next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177448,179784}How many times\Nhave we heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:04.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179784,184539}St. Tail may already be tired\Nof dealing with Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185415,186916}What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186916,190128}You just don't\Nunderstand St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190128,191379}Don't talk like such an authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191379,193423}That's right.\NYou're a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193423,194507}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194507,197969}If you know so much,\Nwhy don't you try to catch St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197969,200138}I'm glad you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:24.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200138,204934}Asuka Jr., or the two of us.\NWho can catch St. Tail first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204934,206477}Let's have a competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206477,208146}That's what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:34.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209731,214152}A Burst Of Laughter!\NThe Detective Team Does a Great Job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215653,216821}The Detective Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216821,220074}Yes! We've formed\Nthe St. Paulia Detective Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:46.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220074,226038}We're going to catch St. Tail and\Nhear Asuka Jr. say, "I lost to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235006,237633}Wait… Wait a minute,\Neveryone…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:02.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238092,242346}Both Kyoko and Ryoko\Nare highly motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242346,244557}But you can never beat Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245558,247852}Right, Asuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247852,249479}What are you doing?!\NGet away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250980,253357}Calm down, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253357,255443}What's with Takamiya's attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255443,257236}Hey, Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257236,259113}Meimi! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259113,262158}Let's join together\Nand catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264452,268664}I'm serving God.\NI can't be involved in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268664,269540}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270124,271542}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272877,275338}All right then.\NKyoko! Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275338,277423}We three will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286891,288810}You said, an emerald?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:53.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289477,293439}My husband is the captain\Nof a ship going abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:57.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293439,297026}The emerald was my present\Nto my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297026,300613}who would finish his last trip\Nand come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301989,307995}It was stolen by a jewel thief who has\Nbeen active recently and targets big houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308913,312416}The police worked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312416,313876}But they can't find any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:20.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315294,320925}I want to get the emerald back at any cost,\Nbefore my husband comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320925,323261}I want to see my husband's\Nlook of surprise…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323261,327473}I'm sure God understands\Nyour feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:36.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330309,336983}According to my sources, the thief is working\Nfor a crooked businessman, Torabatake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336983,340862}Torabatake destroys all evidence\Nlinked to the thefts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340862,345116}He appears to be hiding the jewels\Nin a bronze statue of a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345616,347201}A bronze statue of a dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:51.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347201,351455}You mean the one at the\NAll Sports Center in the Port Area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:56.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351455,356085}That Sports Center was built by Torabatake\Nas a place to hide the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:01.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356669,361048}I'm sure Mrs. Ono's emerald\Nis in the statue of the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361883,366512}No one would ever suspect that\Nthe stolen jewels are hidden in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366512,367680}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368180,370224}It's your show time, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:14.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370224,374645}Let's get back Mrs. Ono's\Nimportant emerald with our power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375104,376105}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376439,379483}All right!\NI'm ready for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394916,397460}We knew that\Nyou'd come! Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397460,398127}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398127,399503}What do you mean, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399503,402089}You came to catch\NSt. Tail, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403132,404550}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405509,409972}In order to deliver a warning note,\NSt. Tail will have to approach Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410806,412516}We're going to catch her then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412516,415186}What a brilliant plan we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:55.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415186,415853}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416312,417897}{\i1}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417897,421275}{\i1}What to do now?\NI can't send a warning note like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435498,436499}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436624,438501}That boy is suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438501,440336}Kyoko! Meimi! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441754,443923}Wait… Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448344,449971}Are you all right, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449971,451430}Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451931,454350}What are you doing?!\NHey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458729,461649}Now we've caught you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461649,463526}Let's see who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464777,466487}Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468322,470032}Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470032,470866}Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471492,474286}We won't let you\Ninterfere, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474286,477581}We're going to catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477581,479333}Speak up, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479333,481252}Admit that the ball\Nwas a warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481627,484171}Are you saying he is St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485840,488426}No! I'm not St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488426,489760}He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490302,493889}That boy is not St. Tail. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497893,498728}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498728,500980}She's right.\NIt's a regular ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500980,503107}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506277,507528}Bullies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507528,509447}You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:37.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511824,517538}What stupid detectives,\Nthinking that child was St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517538,518831}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528549,535139}"Tonight, at the All Sports Center,\NI'll take the bronze dolphin. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535473,537099}What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537683,541896}She got through our surveillance\Nand delivered the warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541896,544106}– St. Tail is very impressive.\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544106,546984}What surveillance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548694,551280}I don't want to hear anything\Nfrom a stupid detective
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551280,554241}who didn't even notice\Na warning note in his own pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554241,555284}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555284,557912}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559538,561791}{\i1}This will be a problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572510,576764}Meimi, how do you think\NSt. Tail comes in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576764,578974}What?!\NWhy do you ask me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579475,581852}Your father is a magician, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581852,586357}So as a magician's daughter I thought\Nyou might know how St. Tail thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586816,590569}You would think so,\Nbut I don't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590569,593906}Are you okay losing\Nto Asuka Jr., Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595741,599286}St. Tail will probably\Ncome this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599703,602248}We'll get you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602498,604834}Watch us, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605626,608129}{\i1}I have to do something\Nabout their fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609213,611674}Please cover for me\Nwhile I'm gone, Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618931,622601}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627314,628607}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630693,632278}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633863,636699}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:54.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650504,654175}Mrs. Ono's husband's ship\Nis arriving at the port tonight, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654175,655134}I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655134,657136}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657136,658304}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658304,660639}I know what Asuka Jr. is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660639,664351}No. The ones you have to be\Ncareful about are Ryoko and Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666020,667730}We know those two well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667730,669648}They may do\Nsomething unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670566,672067}No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674320,677907}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678407,681368}Oh, hello.\NMay I speak with Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682036,683746}Oh, boy, that Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683746,686248}Of all times,\Nhow can she be late now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686624,687708}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687708,689251}It's a phone call from Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690336,691212}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692421,695216}Meimi? Meimi!
Comment: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:36.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:696717,696717}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:41.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:701722,701722}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703515,704767}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704767,706101}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711065,713275}I've got a cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720824,723035}If she's sick, she can't help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:11.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725913,731252}All right then. It's just the two of us.\NLet's catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731252,732253}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746475,747977}– Mr. Torabatake.\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748769,752773}You have arranged for your\Ncompany's security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752773,754858}I appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755609,757653}It's the proper thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757653,761365}This bronze statue\Nis an important asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762700,767955}{\i1}But why is St. Tail\Ntrying to steal this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:57.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771959,777423}{\i1}Not even St. Tail can discover\Nthe secret of this bronze dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777423,778465}Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779550,781510}We've caught a suspicious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782303,783470}Hey! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784096,787433}Sawatari! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789059,790519}What do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790519,793063}I came to take pictures of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793689,794648}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794648,796066}Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796066,797067}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798027,798944}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800237,801989}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815669,817254}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823719,825763}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828057,830601}I won't let you escape,\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832686,836315}St. Paulia Academy\NDetective Team has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838942,840778}You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841403,842279}Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855376,857628}What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857628,859463}Those are raw eggs,\NMr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861882,864885}Stop it!\NThis is St. Tail's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867304,870599}Darn you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870599,871600}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877439,879983}The real St. Tail is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884405,887116}Hey, hey! Wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898669,901171}St. Tail! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906093,907636}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909012,912182}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912391,913934}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932077,933704}What?! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942045,945132}Jewels! My jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957394,958979}Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962900,964359}Is this an emerald?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973535,975037}Mr. Torabatake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:21.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977331,981251}You're Torabatake, aren't you?\NYou're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986298,987174}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987174,989635}Good job, Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990219,994556}Torabatake was\Nsuspected of stealing jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994556,997476}But we had a hard time\Nuncovering any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:41.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997476,1001104}This incident finally gives us\Nthe evidence we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001104,1004316}My perfect hiding place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004316,1006902}Darn you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006902,1008278}Don't forget to cook our dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008278,1009363}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024753,1026588}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027130,1028549}I won't let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029550,1031510}Stop! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031969,1033011}Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034513,1036223}Lock on target! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036682,1037766}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039059,1041186}Oh, no! The match is wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041770,1042646}Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043188,1047025}This is the escape route\NI expected you to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055075,1058078}No! We're going to catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058579,1059496}Plan B!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065919,1067170}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067462,1069631}We've got you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070007,1071883}Now, show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071883,1073594}It's going to be my scoop photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073802,1076054}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086732,1087858}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092988,1094740}Fireworks…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096408,1097701}I'm safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098452,1100454}Oh, where is St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102581,1103749}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105334,1107127}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107127,1109004}Cheer up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109004,1109963}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109963,1112007}We prepared for so long…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112007,1114509}I'm always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:38.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114509,1118555}You did well, St. Paulia Academy's\NDetective Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119806,1121016}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125187,1127439}Thanks for a good photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132069,1136698}{\i1}Did St. Tail do this on purpose\Nin order to get us to make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:19:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136698,1140535}{\i1}But how would she\Nknow about our fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140535,1142204}Ah, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142204,1143789}What's up, Kyoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143789,1145540}We have to go\Nto Meimi to report this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157344,1159888}"I'm returning your\Nimportant emerald."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165310,1167938}– So Meimi caught a cold?\N– Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167938,1170565}Thank you for coming\Nall this way to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170565,1171858}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174695,1176321}Meimi. Your medicine is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:44.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180492,1184204}Thank you.\NBut I don't want it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184579,1187457}Don't be that way.\NYou've got to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:51.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187457,1191753}Ryoko and the others are here, too.\NOpen the door, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192629,1194214}Meimi. Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196717,1199177}Oh, dear!\NSomething is wrong with Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199469,1201179}Oh, dear! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200846,1203765}You don't need to worry.\NShe must be sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215152,1217863}What's the matter, Meimi?\NYou didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217863,1219531}Sorry! I must\Nhave been sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219531,1220741}See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220741,1222451}Oh, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222951,1225203}I'm leaving your medicine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225537,1227622}It seems like you're\Ndealing with the cold well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227622,1229708}Yeah. Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229708,1232461}No, we're the ones who are sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232461,1235172}To tell you the truth,\Nwe let St. Tail escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235297,1238133}Is that so?\NI'm sorry to hear that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240093,1241595}You guys became\Nfriends again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242053,1243138}Kind of…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243138,1246057}But if Asuka Jr. hadn't interfered…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247392,1248769}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248769,1251313}You're the ones\Nwho interfered with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251313,1253106}How can you say that?!
